  <p>Software Developer / HCI Researcher</p>
  <p>
    I am a 26' undergraduate student at <a href="https://www.nd.edu">the University of Notre Dame</a>, persuing <a href="https://cse.nd.edu/undergraduate/">B.S. in Computer Science</a> and <a href="https://acms.nd.edu/undergraduate/">ACMS(suppl.)</a>. 
